data.description: DON'T MISS OUT! County Taxes! No back neighbors! Newly resurfaced pool in 2022! A/C replaced in 2020! Current mortgage is assumable with a low interest rate from 2021! Come look at this Indian River Estates home for sale with a pool. Enjoy the privacy of no neighbors behind you. Large updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Formal dining area and sitting room. Family room with French door that leads to screened pool. Upstairs includes: Large master suite with private bath and 2 closets; 2 additional bedrooms with a shared bath. Shed included. Laundry room and 1 car garage have A/C. Mortgage Assumption is based on current lender acceptance, paperwork available to apply.
